name: Lusamine (Pokemon)
description:
Created by GeomanticArts and please consider supporting the trainer at geoloras.com

Maybe some day Lusamine will look at you the way she looks at Ultra Beasts.

Example images all made with AOM2-7thV3_C_40 at weight 1

'Lusamine [Pokemon], 1girl, white dress, chest gem, multicolored leggings ' example prompt for the normal dress.

LoRA metadata has all the tags used.

The trainer's twitter can be found at https://twitter.com/GeomanticArts

Trained on NAI.
